{"tid":257144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【穆迪降級】港鐵遭降級 高級無抵押及發行人評級降至「Aa2」","createTime":"2017-05-25T04:49:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-25T05:21:52.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4cef5e692e6bc7a4d34e1f876484480f877b1776","tid":257144,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T04:49:43.000Z","msg":"國際評級機構穆迪下調中港評級事宜繼續發酵，今再發表報告指，因應早前將本港主權評級由「Aa1」降至「Aa2」，評級展望由「負面」轉為「穩定」，故亦將港鐵(0066)、香港鐵路有限公司及九廣鐵路公司的高級無抵押及發行人評級，亦由「Aa1」調低至「Aa2」，評級展望亦轉為「穩定」，以反映反映港鐵的基礎信用評估(BCA)仍處於「a2」水平。<br />\n<br />\n但穆迪提到，一旦港鐵的經調整債務對資本比率，維持低於15%，以及債務對 EBITDA 比率維持1.5倍以下，則會考慮上調其BCA 級別。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1495685460138&amp;issue=20170525\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1495685460138%26issue%3D20170525&d=Nfmd4bDsoH5erfxcdPPtTZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=7307eab4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1495685460138%26issue%3D20170525&h=9bea175e\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1495685460138&amp;issue=20170525</a>"},{"pid":"ee9845a5345da37d2945d8043ae531d8e01f43b4","tid":257144,"uid":4811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T05:21:52.000Z","msg":"正常，劏房波啲撚屌都做到財爺，之後陸續有來"}]}